.popup.popup_animatrors-party
	.popup__content
		.popup__close
			+icon("icon-close", "popup__close-icon", "11", "11")
		.popup__body
			.popup__top.popup__top--party
				.popup__heading.popup__heading--party
					h2.popup__title Программа с аниматором
					span.popup__title-city #[strong 3 000 ₽/час]
			.service-slider.service-slider--animators
				ul.service-slider__list.service-slider__list--popup
					li.service-slider__item.service-slider__item--popup
						button.service-slider__button.service-slider__button--active.service-slider__button--popup(type="button" data-tabs-name="_animators-girls" data-tabs-group="animators") Аниматоры девочки
					li.service-slider__item.service-slider__item--popup
						button.service-slider__button.service-slider__button--popup(type="button" data-tabs-name="_animators-boys" data-tabs-group="animators") Аниматоры мальчики
			.service-list__content
				include girls
				include boys

